OL,3,CPresbyterian moderator calls gathering
OL,4,Cover safeguarding failures
OL,6,FThe new leader of the Presbyterian
OL,7,FChurch in Ireland has announced a
OL,8,Fspecial gathering to come together
OL,9,Ffollowing significant safeguarding
OL,10,Ffailings.
OL,12,FOn his first day as moderator Dr
OL,13,FRichard Murray wrote to ministers
OL,14,Fannouncing the special General
OL,15,FAssembly in the wake of the discovery
OL,16,Fof significant failings in the central
OL,17,Fadministration of the church's
OL,18,Fsafeguarding processes.
