OL,3,CPresbyterian moderator calls gathering
OL,4,Cover safeguarding failures
OL,6,FFormer moderator Rev Trevor Gribben
OL,7,Fstood down after a review found
OL,8,F"serious and significant failings" in
OL,9,Fcentral safeguarding functions from
OL,10,Fthe period 2009 to 2022.
OL,12,FIt emerged that failures included
OL,13,Fsituations where the church did not
OL,14,Frespond when people who had suffered
OL,15,Fharm sought help and instances where
OL,16,Foffenders returned to worship in
OL,17,Fchurch but were "inadequately
OL,18,Fmonitored".
