OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,F(PSNI) has launched a criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation into the matter.
OL,10,FThe PCI welcomed the police probe and
OL,11,Fsaid it would be co-operating fully.
OL,13,FOn Monday Dr Murray said the special
OL,14,FGeneral Assembly will take place on
OL,15,FDecember 18.
OL,17,FHe described the purpose as to "come
OL,18,Ftogether as a family before God to
OL,19,Fgrieve and lament for our failings".
