OL,6,F"We will meet in Assembly Buildings,
OL,7,Fin Belfast to call upon God as a
OL,8,Fpeople and to seek His face," he said.
OL,10,F"Please be assured that the purpose of
OL,11,Fthis General Assembly is that we come
OL,12,Ftogether as a family before God to
OL,13,Fgrieve and lament for our failings.
OL,15,F"At the same time, we also want to be
OL,16,Fparticularly mindful of those who have
OL,17,Fbeen harmed as a result of our central
OL,18,Ffailings."
