OL,6,FHe added in his letter: "As I
OL,7,Fconclude, please make this General
OL,8,FAssembly a priority and come to it
OL,9,Fprayerfully so that we may seek the
OL,10,Fface of God together.
OL,12,F"Please pray for those who have been
OL,13,Fhurt by the failings that we have
OL,14,Funcovered, and pray that they will
OL,15,Fhave the courage to seek the help and
OL,16,Fsupport they need.
OL,18,F"Our prayer is also that God would
OL,19,Fhave mercy upon us in the midst of
OL,20,Fthis storm that has not only shocked
OL,21,Fus, but shaken and deeply humbled us."
